%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : Plan generálás

    pending --> dispatched : dispatch_change()
    dispatched --> running : Ralph loop elindul

    running --> verifying : loop-state = done
    running --> stalled : Watchdog L1-L2
    running --> paused : cmd_pause / budget

    stalled --> running : Activity detected
    stalled --> dispatched : Watchdog L3 (redispatch)
    stalled --> failed : Watchdog L4

    verifying --> merge_queue : Minden gate pass
    verifying --> verify_failed : Gate fail
    verify_failed --> running : Retry (< max)
    verify_failed --> failed : Retry exhausted

    paused --> running : cmd_resume
    paused --> running : Budget available

    merge_queue --> merging : Policy allows
    merging --> merged : Merge OK
    merging --> merge_blocked : Conflict
    merge_blocked --> merging : Retry / LLM fix

    merged --> smoking : smoke_command
    smoking --> completed : Smoke pass
    smoking --> smoke_failed : Smoke fail
    smoke_failed --> running : Smoke fix retry

    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
    skipped --> [*]

    pending --> skipped : Dependency failed

    note right of running : 15s poll ciklus\nToken tracking\nWatchdog figyelés
    note right of verifying : Test → Review → Verify\n→ Smoke → E2E
    note right of merge_queue : eager / checkpoint / manual
